# Reusable Widgets — obm_gen_with_ai

> Import path: `{{IMPORT_COMPONENTS}}`
> Variables: See `_project_config.mdc`. Key values: `{{BTN_CLASS}}`, `{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}`, `{{TEXT_WIDGET}}`, `{{SVG_HELPER}}`, `{{CONSUMER_BASE}}`, `{{SELECTOR_BASE}}`, `{{PROGRESS_LOAD}}`, `{{M_SHOW_DIALOG}}`, `{{M_SHOW_TOAST}}`, `{{DIALOG_TYPE_ENUM}}`, `{{TOAST_TYPE_ENUM}}`, `{{I18N_CLASS}}`, `{{BRAND}}`, `{{TEXT_DEFAULT}}`, `{{TEXT_LIGHT_GREY}}`, `{{DIVIDER}}`, `{{ERROR}}`.

## Golden Rule

> **Check this list and `{{IMPORT_COMPONENTS}}` before writing any widget.**
> If it already exists, reuse it. Consistency + less surface area for bugs.

## {{BTN_CLASS}}

File: `lib/core/components/core_button.dart`

```dart
{{BTN_CLASS}}(
  text: {{I18N_CLASS}}.save,                  // default ""
  onPress: () {},                           // required
  backgroundColor: {{BRAND}},               // default Colors.blueAccent
  textColor: Colors.white,
  width: double.infinity,                   // optional
  height: 48,                              // optional
  borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8),    // default: circular(4) in code + extra circular(16) wrapper
  borderWidth: 1.0,
  colorBorder: Colors.transparent,
  padding: const EdgeInsets.all(10),        // default
  margin: const EdgeInsets.all(0),
  isLeftIcon: false,
  isRightIcon: false,
  iconLeft: Icons.add,
  iconRight: Icons.arrow_forward,
  sizeIcon: 15,
  colorIcon: Colors.white,
  marginLeftIcon: 8,
  styleText: const TextStyle(fontSize: 16, fontWeight: FontWeight.w600),
  maxLineTextButton: 1,
  alignmentText: Alignment.center,
  shadowColor: Colors.transparent,
  elevation: const WidgetStatePropertyAll(0),
)
```

## {{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}} (file `core_text.dart`)

```dart
// Predefined styles
Text('Hello', style: {{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}.common);
Text('Required', style: {{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}.labelTextRequiredStyle);
Text('Hint', style: {{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}.hintTextStyle);
Text('Disabled', style: {{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}.disableTextStyle);

// Factory widget
{{TEXT_WIDGET}}(
  title: 'Title',
  fontSize: 16,
  fontWeight: FontWeight.w600,
  color: {{BRAND}},
  maxLines: 2,
  overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis,
  textAlign: TextAlign.center,
);

// Per-weight style builders
{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}().getRegularStyle(fontSize: 14, color: Colors.black);
{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}().getMediumStyle(fontSize: 14, color: Colors.black);
{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}().getSemiBoldStyle(fontSize: 14, color: Colors.black);
{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}().getBoldStyle(fontSize: 14, color: Colors.black);
{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}().getLightStyle(fontSize: 14, color: Colors.black);
```

## {{SVG_HELPER}}()

File: `lib/core/components/image.dart`

```dart
{{SVG_HELPER}}(
  'assets/images/ic_success_dialog.svg',
  width: 120,
  height: 120,
  color: {{BRAND}},
  package: 'modulevnelife',    // optional, for assets from other packages
  active: true,               // false → grayscale
)
```

Always use `{{SVG_HELPER}}()` for local SVG. Never call `SvgPicture.asset` directly.

## State Consumers

```dart
// PREFERRED — auto-switches on {{STATE_TYPE}}
{{CONSUMER_BASE}}<XxxService, XxxProvider>(
  contextParent: context,
  onRepositoryLoading: (_) =>
      const Center(child: CircularProgressIndicator()),
  onRepositorySuccess: (repo) => _buildList(repo as XxxProvider),
  onRepositoryError: (repo) => _buildError(repo as XxxProvider),
  onRepositoryNoData: (repo) => const _EmptyView(),
)

// ONLY when watching a specific field
{{SELECTOR_BASE}}<XxxProvider>(
  selector: (ctx, p) => p.title,
  contextParrent: context,
  onRepository: (ctx, repo) =>
      Text((repo as XxxProvider).title),
)

// Low-level
context.select<XxxProvider, int>((p) => p.items.length);
context.read<XxxProvider>().fetchItems();
```

