## When to Create a New Widget

Create a new widget only when **all 3 conditions are met**:

1. No existing widget in this list or `{{IMPORT_COMPONENTS}}` fulfills the need.
2. The widget is used in **2 or more places**.
3. The widget has a **clear API** (props documented, no leaked external state).

If used only once, keep it inline in the body widget.

## Review Checklist for New Widget in PR

- [ ] Searched `{{IMPORT_COMPONENTS}}` first.
- [ ] Used in at least 2 places.
- [ ] Props are clearly named and documented.
- [ ] Uses `{{BRAND}}`, `{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}.*`, `{{I18N_GETTER}}`.
- [ ] If screen-level reusable component → consider placing in `{{IMPORT_COMPONENTS}}` for future reuse.
